metadata.description: Our much loved Welcome Video was completely recreated by our content crew giving it a 1980s VHS vibe! This is the original copy, no other copies will ever be made available for sale. We imagined this as a unique opportunity for one lucky Saitama Inu fan to own a piece of our history that will become even more valuable in the future, as our community keeps growing. This token is resellable.
